thread.title: Erin

author: Erin
title: Erin
text:
Mark and his team made selling our house an absolute breeze. They arranged and coordinated tradespeople, and ran an incredibly successful campaign all to schedule in a very tight timeframe. And the auction result exceeded our wildest expectations!
Mark's personality and enthusiasm are easily seen, and he has the professionalism and dedication to match. He's also a very entertaining auctioneer! We would heartily recommend selling your property through him.
